{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":230,"text":"I can't help but this wish:"},{"time":1583,"text":"to think about when you're a little kid,\nand all your friends ask you,"},{"time":6040,"text":"\"If a genie could give you\none wish in the world,"},{"time":8652,"text":"what would it be?\""},{"time":10183,"text":"And I always answered,"},{"time":11596,"text":"\"Well, I'd want the wish"},{"time":12930,"text":"to have the wisdom to know\nexactly what to wish for.\""},{"time":16772,"text":"Well, then you'd be screwed,"},{"time":18147,"text":"because you'd know what to wish for,\nand you'd use up your wish,"},{"time":21186,"text":"and now, since we only have one wish --\nunlike last year they had three wishes --"},{"time":25033,"text":"I'm not going to wish for that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26543,"text":"So let's get to what I would like,\nwhich is world peace."},{"time":31570,"text":"And I know what you're thinking:"},{"time":33626,"text":"You're thinking, \"The poor girl up there,"},{"time":35614,"text":"she thinks she's at a beauty pageant."},{"time":37415,"text":"She's not. She's at the TED Prize.\""},{"time":39690,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":42824,"text":"But I really do think it makes sense."},{"time":45244,"text":"And I think that\nthe first step to world peace"},{"time":47863,"text":"is for people to meet each other."},{"time":49707,"text":"I've met a lot of different\npeople over the years,"},{"time":52219,"text":"and I've filmed some of them,"},{"time":53645,"text":"from a dotcom executive in New York\nwho wanted to take over the world,"},{"time":58565,"text":"to a military press officer in Qatar,"},{"time":61000,"text":"who would rather not take over the world."},{"time":63529,"text":"If you've seen the film\n\"Control Room\" that was sent out,"},{"time":66238,"text":"you'd understand a little bit why."},{"time":67887,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":69062,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":70244,"text":"Wow! Some of you watched it.\nThat's great. That's great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73540,"text":"So basically what I'd like\nto talk about today"},{"time":78134,"text":"is a way for people to travel,"},{"time":81000,"text":"to meet people in a different way than --"},{"time":85000,"text":"because you can't travel\nall over the world at the same time."},{"time":88000,"text":"And a long time ago --\nwell, about 40 years ago --"},{"time":93260,"text":"my mom had an exchange student."},{"time":96897,"text":"And I'm going to show you\nslides of the exchange student."},{"time":99739,"text":"This is Donna."},{"time":100914,"text":"This is Donna at the Statue of Liberty."},{"time":104446,"text":"This is my mother and aunt\nteaching Donna how to ride a bike."},{"time":108538,"text":"This is Donna eating ice cream."},{"time":111284,"text":"And this is Donna teaching my aunt\nhow to do a Filipino dance."},{"time":117882,"text":"I really think as the world\nis getting smaller,"},{"time":120123,"text":"it becomes more and more important"},{"time":121790,"text":"that we learn each other's dance moves,"},{"time":123676,"text":"that we meet each other,\nwe get to know each other,"},{"time":126106,"text":"we are able to figure out\na way to cross borders,"},{"time":129769,"text":"to understand each other, to understand\npeople's hopes and dreams,"},{"time":132917,"text":"what makes them laugh and cry."},{"time":134397,"text":"And I know that we can't\nall do exchange programs,"},{"time":137442,"text":"and I can't force everybody to travel;"},{"time":139291,"text":"I've already talked about that\nto Chris and Amy,"},{"time":141634,"text":"and they said that\nthere's a problem with this:"},{"time":143860,"text":"You can't force people, free will."},{"time":145619,"text":"And I totally support that,\nso we're not forcing people to travel."},{"time":148750,"text":"But I'd like to talk\nabout another way to travel"},{"time":151028,"text":"that doesn't require\na ship or an airplane,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and just requires a movie camera,\na projector and a screen."},{"time":159000,"text":"And that's what I'm going\nto talk to you about today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163857,"text":"I was asked that I speak a little bit\nabout where I personally come from,"},{"time":168612,"text":"and Cameron, I don't know how\nyou managed to get out of that one,"},{"time":171739,"text":"but I think that building bridges\nis important to me"},{"time":176000,"text":"because of where I come from."},{"time":178171,"text":"I'm the daughter of an American mother"},{"time":181574,"text":"and an Egyptian-Lebanese-Syrian father."},{"time":184709,"text":"So I'm the living product\nof two cultures coming together."},{"time":188805,"text":"No pun intended."},{"time":189981,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":191012,"text":"And I've also been called,"},{"time":192293,"text":"as an Egyptian-Lebanese-Syrian American\nwith a Persian name,"},{"time":195166,"text":"the \"Middle East Peace Crisis.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":197080,"text":"So maybe me starting to take\npictures was some kind of way"},{"time":201580,"text":"to bring both sides\nof my family together --"},{"time":205056,"text":"a way to take the worlds with me,\na way to tell stories visually."},{"time":210453,"text":"It all kind of started that way,"},{"time":212073,"text":"but I think that I really realized\nthe power of the image"},{"time":215693,"text":"when I first went\nto the garbage-collecting village"},{"time":218929,"text":"in Egypt, when I was about 16."},{"time":221326,"text":"My mother took me there."},{"time":223905,"text":"She's somebody who believes strongly\nin community service,"},{"time":226688,"text":"and decided that this was something\nthat I needed to do."},{"time":229355,"text":"And so I went there and I met\nsome amazing women there."},{"time":233000,"text":"There was a center there,"},{"time":235954,"text":"where they were teaching\npeople how to read and write,"},{"time":239016,"text":"and get vaccinations\nagainst the many diseases"},{"time":241254,"text":"you can get from sorting through garbage."},{"time":243373,"text":"And I began teaching there."},{"time":244962,"text":"I taught English, and I met\nsome incredible women there."},{"time":248000,"text":"I met people that live\nseven people to a room,"},{"time":252812,"text":"barely can afford their evening meal,"},{"time":255168,"text":"yet lived with this strength\nof spirit and sense of humor"},{"time":258715,"text":"and just incredible qualities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261421,"text":"I got drawn into this community\nand I began to take pictures there."},{"time":265199,"text":"I took pictures of weddings\nand older family members --"},{"time":272000,"text":"things that they wanted memories of."},{"time":275141,"text":"About two years after I started\ntaking these pictures,"},{"time":278570,"text":"the UN Conference\non Population and Development"},{"time":283000,"text":"asked me to show them at the conference."},{"time":285920,"text":"So I was 18; I was very excited."},{"time":288892,"text":"It was my first exhibit of photographs\nand they were all put up there,"},{"time":294273,"text":"and after about two days,\nthey all came down except for three."},{"time":300789,"text":"People were very upset,"},{"time":302663,"text":"very angry that I was showing\nthese dirty sides of Cairo,"},{"time":306297,"text":"and why didn't I cut\nthe dead donkey out of the frame?"},{"time":309778,"text":"And as I sat there, I got very depressed."},{"time":312039,"text":"I looked at this big empty wall\nwith three lonely photographs"},{"time":317661,"text":"that were, you know,\nvery pretty photographs"},{"time":321939,"text":"and I was like, \"I failed at this.\""},{"time":324854,"text":"But I was looking at this intense\nemotion and intense feeling"},{"time":330001,"text":"that had come out of people\njust seeing these photographs."},{"time":333478,"text":"Here I was, this 18-year-old pipsqueak\nthat nobody listened to,"},{"time":336483,"text":"and all of a sudden,\nI put these photographs on the wall,"},{"time":339285,"text":"and there were arguments,\nand they had to be taken down."},{"time":341941,"text":"And I saw the power of the image,\nand it was incredible."},{"time":345313,"text":"And I think the most important reaction\nthat I saw there was actually from people"},{"time":349171,"text":"that would never have gone\nto the garbage village themselves,"},{"time":352070,"text":"that would never have seen\nthat the human spirit could thrive"},{"time":354959,"text":"in such difficult circumstances."},{"time":357067,"text":"And I think it was at that point"},{"time":358623,"text":"that I decided I wanted to use\nphotography and film"},{"time":362909,"text":"to somehow bridge gaps,\nto bridge cultures,"},{"time":365375,"text":"bring people together, cross borders."},{"time":370713,"text":"And so that's what really\nkind of started me off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374373,"text":"Did a stint at MTV, made a film\ncalled \"Startup.com,\""},{"time":377702,"text":"and I've done a couple of music films."},{"time":382000,"text":"But in 2003, when the war\nin Iraq was about to start,"},{"time":389465,"text":"it was a very surreal feeling for me,"},{"time":391701,"text":"because before the war started,"},{"time":393601,"text":"there was kind of this media war\nthat was going on."},{"time":396037,"text":"And I was watching television in New York,"},{"time":398077,"text":"and there seemed to be just one\npoint of view that was coming across,"},{"time":401738,"text":"and the coverage went\nfrom the US State Department"},{"time":406589,"text":"to embedded troops."},{"time":409087,"text":"And what was coming across on the news"},{"time":411731,"text":"was that there was going to be this\nclean war and precision bombings,"},{"time":416000,"text":"and the Iraqis would be greeting\nthe Americans as liberators,"},{"time":419798,"text":"and throwing flowers at their feet\nin the streets of Baghdad."},{"time":423098,"text":"And I knew that there\nwas a completely other story"},{"time":425995,"text":"that was taking place in the Middle East,\nwhere my parents were."},{"time":429037,"text":"I knew that there was\na completely other story being told,"},{"time":432126,"text":"and I was thinking, \"How are people\nsupposed to communicate with each other"},{"time":435682,"text":"when they're getting completely\ndifferent messages,"},{"time":438099,"text":"and nobody knows\nwhat the other's being told?"},{"time":440230,"text":"How are people supposed to have\nany kind of common understanding"},{"time":443271,"text":"or know how to move together\ninto the future?"},{"time":445930,"text":"So I knew that I had to go there."},{"time":448202,"text":"I just wanted to be in the center."},{"time":450266,"text":"I had no plan. I had no funding."},{"time":452791,"text":"I didn't even have a camera at the time --\nI had somebody bring it there,"},{"time":457000,"text":"because I wanted\nto get access to Al Jazeera,"},{"time":460000,"text":"George Bush's favorite channel,"},{"time":462000,"text":"and a place which I was very curious\nabout because it's disliked"},{"time":467265,"text":"by many governments across the Arab world,"},{"time":469780,"text":"and also called the mouthpiece\nof Osama Bin Laden"},{"time":473406,"text":"by some people in the US government."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475611,"text":"So I was thinking, this station\nthat's hated by so many people"},{"time":479909,"text":"has to be doing something right."},{"time":481466,"text":"I've got to go see what this is all about."},{"time":484999,"text":"And I also wanted to go see\nCentral Command,"},{"time":487120,"text":"which was 10 minutes away."},{"time":488688,"text":"And that way, I could get access\nto how this news was being created --"},{"time":494000,"text":"on the Arab side, reaching the Arab world,"},{"time":496232,"text":"and on the US and Western side,\nreaching the US."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499015,"text":"And when I went there and sat there,"},{"time":500780,"text":"and met these people\nthat were in the center of it,"},{"time":503861,"text":"and sat with these characters,"},{"time":507491,"text":"I met some surprising,\nvery complex people."},{"time":511792,"text":"And I'd like to share with you\na little bit of that experience"},{"time":516000,"text":"of when you sit with somebody"},{"time":517498,"text":"and you film them, and you listen to them,"},{"time":519546,"text":"and you allow them more\nthan a five-second sound bite."},{"time":523314,"text":"The amazing complexity of people emerges."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531701,"text":"Samir Khader: Business as usual."},{"time":534000,"text":"Iraq, and then Iraq, and then Iraq."},{"time":540897,"text":"But between us, if I'm offered\na job with Fox, I'll take it."},{"time":550977,"text":"To change the Arab nightmare\ninto the American dream."},{"time":560979,"text":"I still have that dream."},{"time":563229,"text":"Maybe I will never be able to do it,"},{"time":566000,"text":"but I have plans for my children."},{"time":570524,"text":"When they finish high school,"},{"time":571938,"text":"I will send them to America\nto study there."},{"time":573978,"text":"I will pay for their study."},{"time":576641,"text":"And they will stay there."},{"time":585175,"text":"Josh Rushing: The night they showed\nthe POWs and the dead soldiers --"},{"time":589052,"text":"Al Jazeera showed them --"},{"time":590292,"text":"it was powerful, because America\ndoesn't show those kinds of images."},{"time":593520,"text":"Most of the news in America\nwon't show really gory images"},{"time":596229,"text":"and this showed American soldiers\nin uniform, strewn about a floor,"},{"time":599428,"text":"a cold tile floor."},{"time":600627,"text":"And it was revolting."},{"time":603387,"text":"It was absolutely revolting."},{"time":604897,"text":"It made me sick at my stomach."},{"time":606373,"text":"And then what hit me was,\nthe night before,"},{"time":609723,"text":"there had been some kind\nof bombing in Basra,"},{"time":613342,"text":"and Al Jazeera had shown\nimages of the people."},{"time":618182,"text":"And they were equally, if not more,\nhorrifying -- the images were."},{"time":622400,"text":"And I remember having seen it\nin the Al Jazeera office,"},{"time":625039,"text":"and thought to myself, \"Wow, that's gross."},{"time":628252,"text":"That's bad.\""},{"time":630067,"text":"And then going away, and probably\neating dinner or something."},{"time":633001,"text":"And it didn't affect me as much."},{"time":634628,"text":"So, the impact that had on me --"},{"time":637475,"text":"me realizing that I just saw\npeople on the other side,"},{"time":641157,"text":"and those people in the Al Jazeera office"},{"time":643993,"text":"must have felt the way\nI was feeling that night,"},{"time":646304,"text":"and it upset me on a profound level"},{"time":649447,"text":"that I wasn't as bothered\nas much the night before."},{"time":653650,"text":"It makes me hate war."},{"time":655650,"text":"But it doesn't make me believe\nthat we're in a world"},{"time":658252,"text":"that can live without war yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659787,"text":"Jehane Noujaim: I was overwhelmed\nby the response of the film."},{"time":662904,"text":"We didn't know whether\nit would be able to get out there."},{"time":665611,"text":"We had no funding for it."},{"time":666851,"text":"We were incredibly lucky\nthat it got picked up."},{"time":671053,"text":"And when we showed the film"},{"time":673558,"text":"in both the United States\nand the Arab world,"},{"time":676258,"text":"we had such incredible reactions."},{"time":678399,"text":"It was amazing to see how people\nwere moved by this film."},{"time":681431,"text":"In the Arab world --"},{"time":683618,"text":"and it's not really by the film,\nit's by the characters --"},{"time":686479,"text":"I mean, Josh Rushing was\nthis incredibly complex person"},{"time":690534,"text":"who was thinking about things."},{"time":692085,"text":"And when I showed the film\nin the Middle East,"},{"time":694378,"text":"people wanted to meet Josh."},{"time":697000,"text":"He kind of redefined us\nas an American population."},{"time":700894,"text":"People started to ask me,\n\"Where is this guy now?\""},{"time":705000,"text":"Al Jazeera offered him a job."},{"time":707023,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":709000,"text":"And Samir, on the other hand,"},{"time":711274,"text":"was also quite an interesting character\nfor the Arab world to see,"},{"time":714632,"text":"because it brought out the complexities\nof this love-hate relationship"},{"time":718313,"text":"that the Arab world has with the West."}]},{"cues":[{"time":721257,"text":"In the United States, I was blown away\nby the motivations,"},{"time":726472,"text":"the positive motivations\nof the American people"},{"time":729320,"text":"when they'd see this film."},{"time":731414,"text":"You know, we're criticized abroad"},{"time":733033,"text":"for believing we're the saviors\nof the world in some way,"},{"time":736548,"text":"but the flip side of it is that, actually,"},{"time":739891,"text":"when people do see\nwhat is happening abroad"},{"time":742249,"text":"and people's reactions\nto some of our policy abroad,"},{"time":745000,"text":"we feel this power, that we need to --"},{"time":747294,"text":"we feel like we have to get\nthe power to change things."},{"time":749913,"text":"And I saw this with audiences."},{"time":751492,"text":"This woman came up to me\nafter the screening and said,"},{"time":755272,"text":"\"You know, I know this is crazy."},{"time":756889,"text":"I saw the bombs being loaded\non the planes,"},{"time":758936,"text":"I saw the military going out to war,"},{"time":760699,"text":"but you don't understand\npeople's anger towards us"},{"time":763085,"text":"until you see the people in the hospitals\nand the victims of the war,"},{"time":767272,"text":"and how do we get out of this bubble?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":769241,"text":"How do we understand what\nthe other person is thinking?\""},{"time":774000,"text":"Now, I don't know whether\na film can change the world."},{"time":778095,"text":"But I know the power of it,"},{"time":780596,"text":"I know that it starts people thinking\nabout how to change the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784613,"text":"Now, I'm not a philosopher,"},{"time":786327,"text":"so I feel like I shouldn't\ngo into great depth on this,"},{"time":789209,"text":"but let film speak for itself\nand take you to this other world."},{"time":793000,"text":"Because I believe that film has\nthe ability to take you across borders,"},{"time":797124,"text":"I'd like you to just sit back\nand experience for a couple of minutes"},{"time":801166,"text":"being taken into another world."},{"time":803000,"text":"And these couple clips take you inside\nof two of the most difficult conflicts"},{"time":808731,"text":"that we're faced with today."},{"time":811578,"text":"[The last 48 hours of two\nPalestinian suicide bombers.]"},{"time":816520,"text":"[Paradise Now]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":819927,"text":"[Man: As long as there is injustice,\nsomeone must make a sacrifice!]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":823150,"text":"[Woman: That's no\nsacrifice, that's revenge!]"},{"time":826657,"text":"[If you kill, there's no difference\nbetween victim and occupier.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":831763,"text":"[Man: If we had airplanes, we wouldn't\nneed martyrs, that's the difference.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":837554,"text":"[Woman: The difference is that the Israeli\nmilitary is still stronger.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":842788,"text":"[Man: Then let us be equal in death.]"},{"time":845000,"text":"[We still have Paradise.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":847105,"text":"[Woman: There is no Paradise!\nIt only exists in your head!]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":850051,"text":"[Man: God forbid!]"},{"time":852798,"text":"[May God forgive you.]"},{"time":855000,"text":"[If you were not Abu Azzam's daughter ...]"},{"time":859932,"text":"[Anyway, I'd rather have Paradise\nin my head than live in this hell!]"},{"time":863215,"text":"[In this life, we're dead anyway.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":866650,"text":"[One only chooses bitterness\nwhen the alternative is even bitterer.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":872999,"text":"[Woman: And what about us?\nThe ones who remain?]"},{"time":875518,"text":"[Will we win that way?]"},{"time":879280,"text":"[Don't you see what you're\ndoing is destroying us?]"},{"time":883789,"text":"[And that you give Israel\nan alibi to carry on?]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":887946,"text":"[Man: So with no alibi, Israel will stop?]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":890361,"text":"[Woman: Perhaps. We have\nto turn it into a moral war.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":894593,"text":"[Man: How, if Israel has no morals?]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":897890,"text":"[Woman: Be careful!]"},{"time":901440,"text":"[And the real people building\npeace through non-violence]"},{"time":908025,"text":"[Encounter Point]"},{"time":911856,"text":"Video: (Ambulance siren)\n[Tel Aviv, Israel 1996]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":917014,"text":"[Tzvika: My wife Ayelet\ncalled me and said, ]"},{"time":919487,"text":"[\"There was a suicide\nbombing in Tel Aviv.\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":922915,"text":"[Ayelet: What do you know\nabout the casualties?]"},{"time":925451,"text":"[Tzvika off-screen:\nWe're looking for three girls.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":928295,"text":"[We have no information.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":929595,"text":"[Ayelet: One is wounded here, but we\nhaven't heard from the other three.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":934000,"text":"[Tzvika: I said, \"OK,\nthat's Bat-Chen, that's my daughter.]"},{"time":937949,"text":"[Are you sure she is dead?\"]"},{"time":940157,"text":"[They said yes.]"},{"time":941335,"text":"Video: (Police siren\nand shouting over megaphone)"},{"time":943661,"text":"[Bethlehem, Occupied\nPalestinian Territories, 2003]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":950000,"text":"[George: On that day, at around 6:30]"},{"time":953000,"text":"[I was driving with my wife\nand daughters to the supermarket.]"},{"time":961000,"text":"[When we got to here ...]"},{"time":965048,"text":"[we saw three Israeli military jeeps\nparked on the side of the road.]"},{"time":971300,"text":"[When we passed by the first jeep ...]"},{"time":973620,"text":"[they opened fire on us.]"},{"time":976896,"text":"[And my 12-year-old daughter Christine]"},{"time":979763,"text":"[was killed in the shooting.]"},{"time":982793,"text":"[Bereaved Families Forum, Jerusalem]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":993774,"text":"[Tzvika: I'm the headmaster\nfor all parts.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":996866,"text":"[George: But there is a teacher\nthat is in charge?]"},{"time":999288,"text":"[Tzvika: Yes, I have assistants.]"},{"time":1001228,"text":"[I deal with children all the time.]"},{"time":1004277,"text":"[One year after their daughters' deaths\nboth Tzvika and George join the forum]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1010963,"text":"[George: At first, I thought\nit was a strange idea.]"},{"time":1016246,"text":"[But after thinking logically about it, ]"},{"time":1018688,"text":"[I didn't find any reason\nwhy not to meet them]"},{"time":1024320,"text":"[and let them know of our suffering.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029774,"text":"[Tzvika: There were\nmany things that touched me.]"},{"time":1033242,"text":"[We see that there are Palestinians\nwho suffered a lot, who lost children,]"},{"time":1038381,"text":"[and still believe in the peace\nprocess and in reconciliation.]"},{"time":1042000,"text":"[If we who lost what is most precious\ncan talk to each other,]"},{"time":1045649,"text":"[and look forward to a better future,]"},{"time":1048800,"text":"[then everyone else must do so, too.]"},{"time":1055749,"text":"[From South Africa:\nA Revolution Through Music]"},{"time":1060320,"text":"[Amandla]"},{"time":1062937,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1064000,"text":"(Video) Man: Song is something\nthat we communicated with people"},{"time":1067492,"text":"who otherwise would not have\nunderstood where we're coming from."},{"time":1072071,"text":"You could give them\na long political speech,"},{"time":1074738,"text":"they would still not understand."},{"time":1077038,"text":"But I tell you, when you finish that song,"},{"time":1079761,"text":"people will be like, \"Damn, I know\nwhere you niggas are coming from."},{"time":1083766,"text":"I know where you guys are coming from."},{"time":1085837,"text":"Death unto apartheid!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1087989,"text":"Narrator: It's about\nthe liberation struggle."},{"time":1091362,"text":"It's about those children\nwho took to the streets --"},{"time":1094833,"text":"fighting, screaming,\n\"Free Nelson Mandela!\""},{"time":1099477,"text":"It's about those unions\nwho put down their tools"},{"time":1104376,"text":"and demanded freedom."},{"time":1107022,"text":"Yes. Yes!"},{"time":1109681,"text":"(Music and singing)"},{"time":1114547,"text":"(Singing) Freedom!"},{"time":1117589,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1121372,"text":"Jehane Noujaim: I think everybody's\nhad that feeling of sitting in a theater,"},{"time":1125038,"text":"in a dark room, with other strangers,\nwatching a very powerful film,"},{"time":1129308,"text":"and they felt that feeling\nof transformation."},{"time":1132340,"text":"And what I'd like to talk about is"},{"time":1135316,"text":"how can we use that feeling"},{"time":1138000,"text":"to actually create\na movement through film?"},{"time":1142837,"text":"I've been listening to the talks\nin the conference,"},{"time":1147382,"text":"and Robert Wright said yesterday"},{"time":1149461,"text":"that if we have an appreciation\nfor another person's humanity,"},{"time":1153053,"text":"then they will have\nan appreciation for ours."},{"time":1155609,"text":"And that's what this is about."},{"time":1157431,"text":"It's about connecting people through film,"},{"time":1160000,"text":"getting these independent\nvoices out there."},{"time":1163400,"text":"Now, Josh Rushing actually\nended up leaving the military"},{"time":1168208,"text":"and taking a job with Al Jazeera."},{"time":1170279,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1171596,"text":"So his feeling is that\nhe's at Al Jazeera International"},{"time":1175207,"text":"because he feels like\nhe can actually use media"},{"time":1178000,"text":"to bridge the gap between East and West."},{"time":1181415,"text":"And that's an amazing thing."},{"time":1183408,"text":"But I've been trying to think about ways"},{"time":1186264,"text":"to give power to these independent voices,"},{"time":1188948,"text":"to give power to the filmmakers,"},{"time":1190565,"text":"to give power to people who are trying\nto use film for change."},{"time":1195000,"text":"And there are incredible organizations"},{"time":1196873,"text":"that are out there doing this already."},{"time":1199000,"text":"There's Witness,\nthat you heard from earlier."},{"time":1202000,"text":"There's Just Vision, that are working\nwith Palestinians and Israelis"},{"time":1205594,"text":"who are working together for peace,\nand documenting that process"},{"time":1208950,"text":"and getting interviews\nout there and using this film"},{"time":1211750,"text":"to take to Congress to show\nthat it's a powerful tool,"},{"time":1214722,"text":"to show that this is a woman who's had\nher daughter killed in an attack,"},{"time":1219285,"text":"and she believes that there\nare peaceful ways to solve this."},{"time":1222435,"text":"There's Working Films\nand there's Current TV,"},{"time":1226269,"text":"which is an incredible platform\nfor people around the world"},{"time":1229600,"text":"to be able to put their --"},{"time":1230872,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1231900,"text":"Yeah, it's amazing."},{"time":1233075,"text":"I've watched it and I'm blown away by it"},{"time":1236526,"text":"and its potential to bring voices\nfrom around the world --"},{"time":1239834,"text":"independent voices\nfrom around the world --"},{"time":1241866,"text":"and create a truly democratic,\nglobal television."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1245326,"text":"So what can we do to create\na platform for these organizations,"},{"time":1249101,"text":"to create some momentum,"},{"time":1251000,"text":"to get everybody in the world\ninvolved in this movement?"},{"time":1256494,"text":"I'd like for us to imagine for a second."},{"time":1261198,"text":"Imagine a day when you have everyone\ncoming together from around the world."},{"time":1268800,"text":"You have towns and villages\nand theaters --"},{"time":1275732,"text":"all from around the world,"},{"time":1278310,"text":"getting together, and sitting in the dark,"},{"time":1281073,"text":"and sharing a communal\nexperience of watching a film,"},{"time":1285597,"text":"or a couple of films, together."},{"time":1289000,"text":"Watching a film which maybe highlights\na character that is fighting to live,"},{"time":1294506,"text":"or just a character\nthat defies stereotypes,"},{"time":1297704,"text":"makes a joke, sings a song."},{"time":1299797,"text":"Comedies, documentaries, shorts."},{"time":1302100,"text":"This amazing power\ncan be used to change people"},{"time":1304803,"text":"and to bond people together;\nto cross borders,"},{"time":1307651,"text":"and have people feel like\nthey're having a communal experience."},{"time":1311190,"text":"So if you imagine this day\nwhen all around the world,"},{"time":1314160,"text":"you have theaters and places\nwhere we project films."},{"time":1319703,"text":"If you imagine projecting\nfrom Times Square"},{"time":1323322,"text":"to Tahrir Square in Cairo,"},{"time":1326124,"text":"the same film in Ramallah,\nthe same film in Jerusalem."},{"time":1329824,"text":"You know, we've been talking\nto a friend of mine"},{"time":1333148,"text":"about using the side of the Great Pyramid"},{"time":1335846,"text":"and the Great Wall of China."},{"time":1340175,"text":"It's endless what you can imagine,"},{"time":1343000,"text":"in terms of where you can project films"},{"time":1345136,"text":"and where you can have\nthis communal experience."},{"time":1347884,"text":"And I believe that this one day,\nif we can create it,"},{"time":1351000,"text":"this one day can create momentum\nfor all of these independent voices."},{"time":1355375,"text":"There isn't an organization\nwhich is connecting the independent voices"},{"time":1360428,"text":"of the world to get out there,"},{"time":1362000,"text":"and yet I'm hearing\nthroughout this conference"},{"time":1364204,"text":"that the biggest challenge in our future"},{"time":1366258,"text":"is understanding the other,"},{"time":1367894,"text":"and having mutual respect\nfor the other and crossing borders."},{"time":1371851,"text":"And if film can do that,"},{"time":1373748,"text":"and if we can get all of these\ndifferent locations in the world"},{"time":1376950,"text":"to watch these films together --"},{"time":1379578,"text":"this could be an incredible day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1382226,"text":"So we've already made a partnership,"},{"time":1385564,"text":"set up through somebody\nfrom the TED community,"},{"time":1389477,"text":"John Camen, who introduced me\nto Steven Apkon,"},{"time":1392371,"text":"from the Jacob Burns Film Center."},{"time":1395000,"text":"And we started calling up everybody."},{"time":1396914,"text":"And in the last week,"},{"time":1398297,"text":"there have been so many people\nthat have responded to us,"},{"time":1402000,"text":"from as close as Palo Alto,\nto Mongolia and to India."},{"time":1407000,"text":"There are people that want to be\na part of this global day of film;"},{"time":1411580,"text":"to be able to provide a platform\nfor independent voices"},{"time":1415000,"text":"and independent films to get out there."},{"time":1419183,"text":"Now, we've thought\nabout a name for this day,"},{"time":1422870,"text":"and I'd like to share this with you."},{"time":1425353,"text":"Now, the most amazing part\nof this whole process"},{"time":1427638,"text":"has been sharing ideas and wishes,"},{"time":1430990,"text":"and so I invite you\nto give brainstorms onto"},{"time":1434000,"text":"how does this day echo into the future?"},{"time":1437545,"text":"How do we use technology to make\nthis day echo into the future,"},{"time":1442300,"text":"so that we can build community"},{"time":1444000,"text":"and have these communities working\ntogether, through the Internet?"},{"time":1449151,"text":"There was a time, many, many years ago,"},{"time":1451714,"text":"when all of the continents\nwere stuck together."},{"time":1454925,"text":"And we call that landmass Pangea."},{"time":1457894,"text":"So what we'd like to call this day of film\nis Pangea Cinema Day."},{"time":1463614,"text":"And if you just imagine"},{"time":1465137,"text":"that all of these people\nin these towns would be watching,"},{"time":1468644,"text":"then I think that we can\nactually really make a movement"},{"time":1472657,"text":"towards people understanding\neach other better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1475000,"text":"I know that it's very intangible,\ntouching people's hearts and souls,"},{"time":1478843,"text":"but the only way that I know how to do it,"},{"time":1480900,"text":"the only way that I know how to reach out\nto somebody's heart and soul"},{"time":1485509,"text":"all across the world,\nis by showing them a film."},{"time":1488040,"text":"And I know that there are independent\nfilmmakers and films out there"},{"time":1491425,"text":"that can really make this happen."},{"time":1494072,"text":"And that's my wish."},{"time":1496154,"text":"I guess I'm supposed to give you\nmy one-sentence wish,"},{"time":1500625,"text":"but we're way out of time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1503000,"text":"Chris Anderson:\nThat is an incredible wish."},{"time":1505344,"text":"Pangea Cinema: The day\nthe world comes together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1508000,"text":"JN: It's more tangible than world peace,\nand it's certainly more immediate."},{"time":1511742,"text":"But it would be the day that the world\ncomes together through film,"},{"time":1517484,"text":"the power of film."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1518659,"text":"CA: Ladies and gentlemen, Jehane Noujaim."}]}]}